{"tid":1070906,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[TCG] 卡片遊戲- Final Fantasy TCG","createTime":"2019-03-21T03:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T04:58:07.000Z","uid":125632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c10b530bd9ad00246c6cd80d63be5fd4e9808de","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"介紹一個香港比較少人玩的卡片遊戲,<br />\nFinal Fantasy TCG, 簡稱 FF TCG。<br />\n以歷代Final Fantasy 角色作為藍本，<br />\n將職業及角色特性融合於卡片上。<br />\n玩家雙方手持卡組進行回合制對決，以1對1方式對戰的桌上卡片遊戲，最先擊敗對手或耗盡卡片來分勝負。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H30L571.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH30L571.png&h=a5e6de48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFFTCG 曾經多年前推出過舊版，<br />\n但因為平衡問題已成過去式。<br />\n新版與舊版卡比較略有調整，<br />\n重新推出的新版目前有日文、英文及簡體中文版本。<br />\n但版本的更新進度各有差異，今次介紹是以英文為主。<br />\n<br />\n首先雙方各持有1副50張的牌組<br />\n50張包括了4大類卡片：<br />\n前鋒（Forward) 、後衛 (Back Up)、召喚獸 (Summon) 、怪物 (Monster)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nForward : 用來攻擊、防禦對手卡牌<br />\n以牌上Power 點數作為勝負標準，給予對手傷害<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OnhZq8f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOnhZq8f.png&h=e5b29329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBack Up: 相當於Magic 的地牌，用來提供召喚點數、施放技能，干擾對手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4cOjtm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4cOjtm.png&h=f18f8695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSummon: 隨時施放的卡片，大多有可以改寫戰況的能力，因此只有短暫效果時間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HbxCcOx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHbxCcOx.png&h=1dce4b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMonster: 介乎於以上3者的卡種。視不同種類卡片各有不同。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lh0TvAi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLh0TvAi.png&h=36cb1280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊戲玩家先抽5張做手牌，如有需要可重換1 次<br />\n雙方決定先攻後攻<br />\n然後依照以下回合流程去交替對戰<br />\n<br />\nActivate Phase: 將上回合行動完的卡重置<br />\nDraw Phase: 抽2張牌 （第1回合先攻只抽1張）<br />\nMain Phase 1: 佈置手牌於戰場上、施放技能、召喚等<br />\nAttack Phase: 宣告攻擊對手、同樣能施放技能、召喚<br />\nMain Phase 2: 再次佈置手牌、但此階段後就不能攻擊<br />\nEnd Phase: 技能效果終結、丟棄5張以上手牌<br />\n<br />\n以回台制，攻擊對手受到7點傷害、或對方用完所有卡組者勝"},{"pid":"140ceb8ba2754751ed291d501b3982039c86ffc0","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"FF 的世界觀，水晶是重要原素<br />\n遊戲共分為8種水晶屬性<br />\n<br />\n火系（紅）：以火力為中心，技能大多以加強攻擊為主<br />\n冰系（淺藍）：以凍結/停頓對手、或令對手丟棄手牌為主<br />\n風系（綠）：低消耗速攻型卡組<br />\n土系（黃）：技能多以防守為重心，受傷越大能力越強類型<br />\n雷系（紫）：無視傷害、一擊必殺類型卡組<br />\n水系（深藍）：抽牌、讓對手回手牌為主<br />\n光系/暗系： 特殊卡組，只能單體入場<br />\n但大部分都有強勁能力<br />\n<br />\n由於歷代角色太多，為方便個別喜好玩家，SE有推出過各代不同的起始包（Starter Set)。<br />\n<br />\n目前最新的Starter是3月20日推出的<br />\nFF7 starter 2019 及FF14 starter 2019（目前只有日版、英文版）<br />\n日本官網：<a href=\"http://www.square-enix-shop.com/jp/ff-tcg/products/starter.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.square-enix-shop.com%2Fjp%2Fff-tcg%2Fproducts%2Fstarter.html&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=b41f894e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.square-enix-shop.com/jp/ff-tcg/products/starter.html</a><br />\n英文官網：<a href=\"http://fftcg.square-enix-games.com/en/page/releases-2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffftcg.square-enix-games.com%2Fen%2Fpage%2Freleases-2018&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=47e422fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fftcg.square-enix-games.com/en/page/releases-2018</a><br />\n中文官網：<a href=\"http://ff.963.com/products/starter.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fff.963.com%2Fproducts%2Fstarter.html&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=48ce1cca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ff.963.com/products/starter.html</a><br />\n<br />\n所有起始包都由兩種屬性組成，合共50張牌。<br />\n<br />\n當然單純Starter 是不可能滿足玩家，<br />\n因此可以用Booster 來組副屬於自己的Deck <br />\n至今為止Booster 共出了8代（日文）<br />\n英文和中文會比日文稍遲1～2個月。<br />\n特別中文版起步不久還在追趕之前進度。<br />\n<br />\nCard List (能以各系列搜索）<br />\n日本官網：<a href=\"http://www.square-enix-shop.com/jp/ff-tcg/card/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.square-enix-shop.com%2Fjp%2Fff-tcg%2Fcard%2Findex.html&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=13410e4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.square-enix-shop.com/jp/ff-tcg/card/index.html</a><br />\n英文官網：<a href=\"https://fftcg.square-enix-games.com/en/page/cards\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffftcg.square-enix-games.com%2Fen%2Fpage%2Fcards&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=8e2d78d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fftcg.square-enix-games.com/en/page/cards</a><br />\n中文官網：<a href=\"http://ff.963.com/card/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fff.963.com%2Fcard%2Findex.html&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=82edf288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ff.963.com/card/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"879967d15ca7fcec636bf18d872feae1161fbd6d","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:45:59.000Z","msg":"介紹FF14 Starter 2019 , <br />\n前兩天用此Starter 和人對局都有贏過。<br />\n<br />\n整體感覺而言此Starter 相當易上手，<br />\n原因係組卡無太多連鎖性Combo。<br />\n以火系、雷系互相Buff 攻擊力、加速同先制攻擊<br />\n<br />\nDeck 組入面，重點卡算是8-147S<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zKUg8X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zKUg8X.png&h=580e0bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此卡能在移除1名BackUp 的情況下，替自己Buff Haste (加速），First Strike(先制攻擊），Brave (勇氣）及 +1000Power <br />\n面對同級4cost 卡片亦有絕對優勢<br />\n<br />\n其次是8-092C<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXqHq3W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXqHq3W.png&h=c4c257af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在攻擊時能夠Dull (停頓）所有比自己Power低的對手。<br />\n只要善用火系提升Power的特性，就能夠封鎖對手防禦，直接造成傷害"},{"pid":"43179c0b1d7397fb40ec154aa446106357244580","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"香港竟然有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f2b0a1a9e129a8e0e806cd4f105a06549f2a54","tid":1070906,"uid":14349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"幾得意喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4cef8bd8ef38d526b379071af0d75193260631","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43179c0b1d7397fb40ec154aa446106357244580","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"香港竟然有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:41:27.000Z","msg":"有架，不過想更加多人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試下出個介紹Post<br />\n有興趣的朋友可以出來試玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7adc73e2697021551af28632fd9e93c66db87a","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7f2b0a1a9e129a8e0e806cd4f105a06549f2a54","tid":1070906,"uid":14349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"幾得意喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:44:01.000Z","msg":"隻Game 幾有趣又唔會話好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始的時候驚難上手<br />\n玩落就覺得易明同都唔會好唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412275b7d5fb4dd972e9e7c144a68f96cb3d58fc","tid":1070906,"uid":230724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"小眾TCG 好難搵人玩， 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eee3431c2e2c54f844c67f4aa774756e0146de9","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"412275b7d5fb4dd972e9e7c144a68f96cb3d58fc","tid":1070906,"uid":230724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"小眾TCG 好難搵人玩， 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小眾TCG 真係好難搵人<br />\n唯有出Post 宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b2f0e03150b25c40782fb131ffab8efcf75134","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"係唔係剛剛出左新starter?<br />\n見有7同14<br />\n競唔競技到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想主玩8同10"},{"pid":"ba1ce6c37e61e665ac1f056a85b108bbde4f6dc2","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b2f0e03150b25c40782fb131ffab8efcf75134","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"係唔係剛剛出左新starter?<br />\n見有7同14<br />\n競唔競技到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想主玩8同10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"有新Starter <br />\n日文版香港買$90左右<br />\n英文版就未見有<br />\n而於簡體中文就未出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於贏唔贏就要睇下對卡組有幾熟<br />\n有啲高手其求找副牌都可以炒到人一棟都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10代有Starter出過<br />\n8代就需要自組，可以上賣卡的網站買自己的目標"},{"pid":"31ea07dd73a5e9988bd271b87a1a15de1b1157f5","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xWSXEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xWSXEU.jpg&h=a7793443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身諗住手痕開幾包bs<br />\n竟然比我係信和底層見到有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最新果彈仲要最後一盒<br />\n忍唔住手買了<br />\n順手訂左ff7 starter<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下星期有<br />\n<br />\n巴打pm我平時係邊玩啦"},{"pid":"d123cd0bf0373906cbcfc6ea06d926820647424c","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRV4OZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRV4OZQ.jpg&h=8cb32648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔知邊張勁邊張唔勁"},{"pid":"f61fbdd745b2e33b3d179257ddc2caf9935e9847","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d123cd0bf0373906cbcfc6ea06d926820647424c","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRV4OZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRV4OZQ.jpg&h=8cb32648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我唔知邊張勁邊張唔勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:08:39.000Z","msg":"エリアス<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n風系必落之選<br />\n你好好彩抽中兩張最值錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa4ad1415f136a7af8793303eddd9ea9f83eda0","tid":1070906,"uid":125632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31ea07dd73a5e9988bd271b87a1a15de1b1157f5","tid":1070906,"uid":64009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T12:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xWSXEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.